{"tid":677053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[兩大對決] 勝和斬水房 西貢30人大混戰","createTime":"2018-05-25T01:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T02:26:09.000Z","uid":2547,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1325780a0dca55edcaaab15c26936d0ff52ff57f","tid":677053,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T01:05:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-XB2Zt3kn_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-XB2Zt3kn_8&d=8P8rv8oVU7T5x%2FhCmoa3YSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a849852d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-XB2Zt3kn_8</a><br />\n西貢發生黑幫電影情節集體毆鬥案，昨晚約11時30分，一幫有水房背景男子約30人，在翠塘花園一家酒樓分三枱食飯。一行人離開酒樓時，一輛豐田七人車駛至，三名戴口罩刀手下車，持牛肉刀衝向對方揮斬，有人中刀受傷。<br />\n現場消息指，刀手有和勝和背景，由於遇襲一方人多勢眾，撿起垃圾桶及棍做武器還擊，現場殺聲震天，一片混亂。三名刀手不敵，反被對方追打，一名刀手跳海逃生。其餘登上七人車企圖離開，但對方並不放過。<br />\n網上片段顯示，有人登上一輛凌志及拖車，向七人車追撞，將七人車撞停。刀手一方落荒而逃，現場呼喝聲及粗口叫駡不絕，「唔好畀佢走」，刀手及司機被截著無法脫身。<br />\n警方接報大批警員到場控制場面，以及進行捷進行動，當場拘捕三名刀手及司機，一人在一艘小艇上發現、一人匿在一個殘廁內，三名刀手同告受傷。遇襲一方亦有兩人受傷送院。其間有一輛寶馬，司機報稱見有人打鬥，失控撞向石壆，警方懷疑司機屬刀手一方，拘捕帶署調查。警方追緝另一輛白色豐田大霸王七人車，其後在白沙灣碼頭尋獲該輛可疑車。<br />\n據稱，水房前坐館肥威設生日宴，請同門兄弟食飯，離開時中伏。事件中肥威沒有受傷，其後離開現場，警方正聯絡他了解事件。東九龍反黑組接手調查案件。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/090341_3def0c2c508aea360f104a88f7af29ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F090341_3def0c2c508aea360f104a88f7af29ae.jpg&h=6af36fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/090341_cd05e1dcd8b8e092e4dec5449a2da5ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F090341_cd05e1dcd8b8e092e4dec5449a2da5ab.jpg&h=345bce3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/090342_87ca303b7f794e053c66f512a4208b05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F090342_87ca303b7f794e053c66f512a4208b05.jpg&h=97d76098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/090342_202930c0832c829f3f32d3055fa3e3ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F090342_202930c0832c829f3f32d3055fa3e3ac.jpg&h=ff88396b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/090343_8949e6f91ab8a18420ccb22a302d47c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F090343_8949e6f91ab8a18420ccb22a302d47c0.jpg&h=420ff146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d15f53d69d11cd4570b8682488ab1957c11a3af","tid":677053,"uid":2547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T01:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/090749_c3b6dbc0cb8298fbdbf80a896e57c1bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F090749_c3b6dbc0cb8298fbdbf80a896e57c1bd.jpg&h=9bcdaa10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/090750_3def0c2c508aea360f104a88f7af29ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F090750_3def0c2c508aea360f104a88f7af29ae.jpg&h=e4e3a625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/090750_cd05e1dcd8b8e092e4dec5449a2da5ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2